column17:
Product Description

White Diamonds Elizabeth Taylor for women. The success of Elzabeth Taylor's fragrance has motivated many other celebrities to launch their own perfumes. White diamonds is a thin floral fragrance an example of top classics. The harmony of flowers and aldehydes in the top notes together with the sharp base give this fragrance an elegant vintage nuance. The top notes are aldehydes bergamot neroli orange and lily. The heart unites the classical trio violet rose and jasmine accompanied by ylang-ylang Egyptian tuberose and narcissus. The base is composed of oak moss patchouli musk
